# Implementation Plan - Smooth Navigation & UI Transition

## Goal
Replace the "stiff" [VersionSettingsDialog](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#8-1246) pop-up window with a smooth, in-page navigation transition to [VersionSettingsPage](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsPage.xaml.cs#5-12).

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> This changes the UX flow from Modal Dialog to Full Page Navigation.

## Proposed Changes

### [VersionSettingsPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsPage.xaml)
-   **Structure**: Copy the entire layout (Left Tabs + Right Content) from [VersionSettingsDialog.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml).
-   **Animation**: Add `Page.Triggers` for `Loaded` event to trigger a `Storyboard`:
    -   `Opacity`: 0 -> 1 (0.3s)
    -   `RenderTransform.TranslateY`: 50 -> 0 (0.3s, Decelerate)
-   **Styling**: Ensure background matches the main window (transparent/mica) or has a slight overlay.

### [VersionSettingsPage.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsPage.xaml.cs)
-   **Logic**: Port all logic from [VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs):
    -   [ShowOverviewTab](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#79-84), [ShowSettingsTab](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#196-358), [ShowModsTab](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#546-643), [ShowExportTab](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#868-1055), [ShowMaintenanceTab](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#1112-1161).
    -   [ModManager](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/HomePage.xaml.cs#183-232) logic (Enable/Disable/Delete).
    -   `Memory Slider` logic (recently added).
-   **Navigation**: Replace [CloseButton_Click](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSettingsDialog.xaml.cs#1108-1112) with `NavigationService.GoBack()`.

### [HomePage.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/HomePage.xaml.cs)
-   **Navigation**: Update [OpenVersionSettings_Click](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/HomePage.xaml.cs#168-182) and [OpenModManager_Click](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/HomePage.xaml.cs#183-232).
    -   Instead of `new VersionSettingsDialog().ShowDialog()`, use `NavigationService.Navigate(new VersionSettingsPage(...))`.

